Executive Summary
Quencher is an ecommerce based delivery service specializing in Wines and Spirits. Quencher will serve as a Platform to offer a superior luxury experience to customers when shopping for beer, wines and spirits. With a state of the art and easy to use interface, Quencher's legal and of age customers will be able to shop for alcohol and have it delivered to their door within an hour. Alcohol is a 100 billion dollar market with only 1% of sales done online, Quencher will capture the demand and potential market growth in that area.
Market Need / Value Proposition
In the state of Ohio in 2015 there was a record setting 1.1 Billion dollars in liquor sales done. With the online liquor sales only serving as 1.1% of sales done the market potential is enormous. Consumption of liquor in the state of Ohio is growing at a rate of 3.98%. Also the amount of money spent on Alcohol in Ohio has increased by 7.3% this past year. Adding an easy-to-use method offering delivery of product will allow retailers to reach customers that otherwise would not have come to the store due to any inconvenience. Quencher will allow partners to expand their market retention and add consistent repeat new streams of revenue. Quencher API’s the application processing and intellectual property will allow for it to be difficult for other competitors to enter the market.
